-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>开发商鲁本·沃德 (Reuben “Reubs” Ward) 坚定地表示，他完成的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-simpsons-hit-run"><em>《辛普森一家：肇事逃亡》</em></a>翻拍版将永远不会向公众发行。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-simpsons-hit-run-is-a-brilliant-window-into-the-noughties-3210589">《辛普森一家：肇事逃逸》是了解上世纪九十年代的精彩窗口</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据最近在他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/youtube">YouTube</a>频道上发布的名为“THE FINALE”的视频，他的《<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/the-simpsons">辛普森一家</a>：肇事逃亡》</em>翻拍现已完成，展示了从原始资源到<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/unreal-engine">虚幻引擎 5</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-simpsons-hit-run-fan-remake-turning-it-into-an-open-world-game-3256042">重新制作的显着改进</a>。虽然这是一项令人惊叹的成就，也是对经典游戏的热爱，但鲁布斯不会放弃新的和改进的<em>《Hit &amp; Runaway</em> 》。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="结局 - 重制《肇事逃逸》#10" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AHAY-teQoFc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “这是出于娱乐目的的粉丝重制，该游戏将永远无法下载。请不要缠着我可怜的 Discord 模组索要下载链接！”开发者在免责声明中说道（来自<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/awesome-looking-the-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-is-complete-but-it-will-never-be-released"><em>IGN</em></a> ）。</p><p>最初，雷布斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-simpsons-hit-run-has-been-remade-in-just-one-week-3021514">在一周内就重拍了整部<em>《Hit &amp; Run》</em></a> 。然而，这并没有公正地对待游戏，因此开发者花了大约两年的时间将该项目转变为动作冒险游戏的有吸引力的演变。</p><p> <em>《Hit &amp; Run》</em>首席设计师 Joe McGinn 表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-simpsons-hit-and-run-lead-designer-would-love-a-remake-3407609">他“希望”看到这款游戏在更现代的游戏机上得到复兴</a>，制作人 Vlad Ceraldi 补充道，这将是向更多受众介绍这款游戏的“绝佳”机会。</p><p>然而， <em>《辛普森</em>一家》现任联合制作人和游戏联合编剧之一解释说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/making-the-simpsons-hit-run-reboot-happen-would-be-complicated-3007536">有很多因素</a>阻碍了官方重制的可能。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473230" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473230" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473230" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/reubs-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473230" class="wp-caption-text"> 《辛普森一家：肇事逃逸》图片来源：Reubs</figcaption></figure><p>马特·塞尔曼表示：“要实现这一目标，企业需要付出很大的努力。”尽管他支持全球游戏玩家对新<em>《Hit &amp; Run》</em>的看法。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，一位独立开发者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/making-the-simpsons-hit-run-reboot-happen-would-be-complicated-3007536">在最近的游戏盛会中推出了一款新的 3D 游戏，</a>带回了经典游戏<em>SkiFree</em> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/full-the-simpsons-hit-and-run-fan-remake-will-never-be-released-3473207">《辛普森一家：肇事逃逸》粉丝翻拍版的完整版将永远不会发行，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
